{
  "id": "adv_main_02_08_05",
  "title": "東京編2章15話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、今戻りました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry I’m late getting back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 3.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "待ってたぞ、さくら\n練習、始められそうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve been waiting for you‚ Sakura.\nThink you can get straight to practice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 7.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　……でもその前に\n私、サニピのみんなと話さなきゃいけなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! But before I do…\nI have to talk to Sunny Peace about something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 14.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、話してくるといい\nみんな、中で待ってるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. Go talk to them.\nThey’re all waiting inside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n行ってきます、{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!\nWish me luck‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.3333333333658,
          "startTime": 23.5666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 23.35
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……！\nやっと来た。心配したじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura….!\nYou’re finally here. We were worried about you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "昨日の夜から調子悪そうだったけど、大丈夫？\nめずらしく、落ち込んでたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve seemed off since last night. Are you okay?\nWe usually don’t see you so glum.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "うん。ちょっと悩んじゃって\nでも、もう大丈夫だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I was worried about something.\nBut I’m okay now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 42.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本当に？　一応、その……げ、元気づけたくて\n作ってみたんだ、魚魚っとさんのぬいぐるみ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really? I wanted to‚ you know… ch-cheer you up‚\nso I made you something. It’s a Gyogyottosan plushie.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "私も……元気が出る、秘蔵のライブDVD\n特別に永久貸し出し、してもいい。つまり、プレゼント",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here… My treasured DVD that cheers me up.\nI’ll let you borrow it for an extended period. In other words‚ it’s yours.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　二人とも……私のために？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? You both… did that for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9866.666666699999,
          "startTime": 75.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "私だって……甘いものなら元気出るかなって思って\nオススメのお店のマカロンを……はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did something‚ too… I figured something sweet would cheer you up‚\nso I bought some macarons from a recommended shop. Here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "え～、みんな早いわよ……私は今日の夜ごはん\nご馳走にしようって思ってたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heyyy‚ you’re all too fast! And here I was planning on\ncooking her a special dinner tonight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "あはは！　そうだったんだ\nでも……みんな、嬉しいよ。ありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha! Wow‚ I had no idea.\nBut… you guys. I’m so happy. Thanks!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、お互い様よ\nいつもは、私達がさくらに支えてもらってたじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. Thank you.\nYou’ve always been there to support us‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 102.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本当は私も、不安だったんだ\n絶対、スリクスには敵いっこないって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-truth be told… I was scared‚ too.\nI just knew we’d never be as good as IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今回はさくらちゃんまで、落ち込んでる……\nなら、私達がしっかりしないと……って、話してた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this time‚ even you got depressed‚ Sakura-chan…\nSo we had to be strong… that’s what we decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "みんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You guys…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃないと私達、いつまでも成長できないでしょ？\nこれまで以上のパフォーマンスが求められる大会だもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Otherwise‚ we’d never grow‚ right?\nThis tournament is going to ask more of our performance than ever before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんに輝かせてもらってきた分\n私達もさくらちゃんを輝かせてあげたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All the sparkle you’ve given us‚\nwe wanted to give it back to you‚ Sakura-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "私達まで、お、落ち込んでる場合じゃないよねって\n頑張ってみようって、勇気出してみたんだ……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We knew this wasn’t the right time for us to feel d-depressed.\nSo we were brave and decided to push through it. Hehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんだけが……みんなを照らす、太陽じゃない\n私達みんなが、みんなを照らす……太陽になる時",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ you don’t have to be the sun all by yourself.\nWe all become the sun when we help each other shine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "だから……もう、一人で思い詰めたりしないで\n辛い時には、私達にも相談して、頼ってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please‚ don’t keep your worries to yourself anymore.\nWhen you’re having trouble‚ talk to us. Let us help you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "いつだって側にいる。だから、力を合わせましょう\n私達五人で、サニーピースなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re always here for you‚ so let’s work together.\nThe five of us together make up Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "……うん……\nみんな、ありがとう……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nEveryone… thanks!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8466.666666700006,
          "startTime": 192.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 192.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、大丈夫そうだな\n一段と結束も強くなったみたいだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura looks like she’ll be okay.\nAnd she seems to have added another layer of resolve.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 199.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピース、一皮剥けたって感じね\n他の四人も、強くなってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like Sunny Peace has grown a bit.\nThe other four girls have also gotten stronger.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "でも私は、意外とは思ってなかったですよ\nみんなの絆の強さは、近くで見てきたから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’m not at all surprised.\nI’ve seen how strong their bond is up close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……ともあれ、二人ともありがとう\nさくらと話してくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right… Anyway‚ thank you both.\nThanks for having a word with Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。さくらには、沢山助けてもらってきたから\nその恩返しが出来た、と思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no. Sakura has helped me so much in the past.\nI’m just happy I could repay her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで、シード枠争いの強敵は増えちゃったけど\nそれぐらいじゃないと、張り合いないものね……ふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And now we’ve made another formidable foe in the battle for the seeded group spot‚\nbut I need that to motivate me anyway. Hehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
