    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "……え？\n本当に、私達が……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?\nIs it really us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "何、驚いているのよ\n投票の結果なんだから、みんながそう思ったってことよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you so surprised?\nYour competitors voted‚ so that means we all think you deserve it.",
        "id": ""
