      "startTime": 287.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "実際、今日のサニーピースは飛び抜けて良かった\n……凄く悔しいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And it’s true‚ Sunny Peace was by far the best today.\nThough I hate to admit it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "全力で勝ちに行った。でも、届かなかった\n凄かったわ、さくら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tried to win with all my might‚ but it wasn’t enough.\nYou were amazing‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 301.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "さくら達の心底楽しむ、太陽みたいなパフォーマンスは\n私達には真似の出来ない、無二の強さだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your sunny performance‚ full of fun‚\nis something none of us can imitate. It’s a unique power of yours.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "莉央ちゃん……琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san… Kotono-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 312.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、あくまでもシード権を譲っただけよ？\nノーシードでも、当然勝ち上がってみせるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having said that‚ all we’re handing over is the seeded group slot.\nEven without the slot‚ we’re still going to rise to victory.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、本戦で会いましょう\n次は必ず、私達が勝ってみせるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. We’ll see you again in the real tournament.\nAnd next time‚ I promise we will win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 326.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、分かったよ\nこの結果は、二人の想いは、絶対に無駄にしない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay… I understand.\nWe won’t let these results or your feelings go to waste.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 333.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、自分なりに全力でライブを楽しんで\n前に進んでみせるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We will enjoy the concert with all our hearts in our own way‚\nand we’ll go even further.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 342.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_05-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "待ってるからね\n祭典のステージに、みんなと一緒に立てる日を！",
